race.description: Joe Wagner Group F&M Maiden Handicap
race.comment: TE ELCEE (6) settled off speed on debut but kept coming for a close-up fifth then was put away again. Fitter for recent trials and expected to go close fresh. CAITLIN (1) is a former Victorian who trialled a couple of times there but never started. Found a new local yard and has since won a trial leading into debut. Bold showing expected. TUESDAY (10) resumes and strips fitter for two trials. Looks set to run well fresh. LETTIE'S LOT (9) has been kept safe in the early market and has to be included from the inside draw.
